      "summary": "Docker event listener/subscriber routines have no explicit stop contract, so background lifecycle control is pushed into global goroutine orchestration rather than the abstraction interface.",
      "related_files": [
        "goseg/routines/docker.go",
        "goseg/main.go",
        "goseg/routines/version.go"
